title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter Causes Out of Sync
description: Bug 4121 - JarExporter Causes Out of Sync
OB: When using the JarExporter, the exported jar file includes itself, resulting in an out of sync behavior.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Use the JarExporter functionality.
2. Export a jar file.
3. Open the exported jar file and check its contents to see if it includes itself.
